{"tid":505251,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］mac book pro/mac book/iPad 點比較？","createTime":"2017-12-21T02:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T06:10:40.000Z","uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b781a95cb7c3d38dff306981e95008007f5c3c40","tid":505251,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"陳年lap top壞咗&hellip;想轉用apple產品，MacBook pro, MacBook同iPad (包iPad pro)應該買咩好？<br />\n<br />\n主要出差用，要有鍵盤方便文件同電郵&hellip;短期內要出發，下載各種App同軟件方唔方便，係其中一項考慮&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n晤該各位巴打賜教&hellip;"},{"pid":"e061071744e2ed7d1dd355fd59c2b061791657e6","tid":505251,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964a961ff7467432afbba1d3a8a3cf112fc25afb","tid":505251,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9595508c91fa1af51793624aa21eb54359e6e7","tid":505251,"uid":60607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"Macbook 同 macbook Pro 都meet到你要求嘅<br />\n<br />\n12-inch Macbook<br />\nPros: 輕啲, 有特別色<br />\nCons: 貴, keyboard 唔好打, Intel Core m3<br />\n<br />\n13-inch Macbook Pro<br />\nPros: Keyboard 稍為好打, Intel Core i5<br />\nCons: 重啲, 貴啲"},{"pid":"ff3adb9a05028df729876022bac1ed9fb129b76a","tid":505251,"uid":9610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"做普通文書野買ipad配個keyboard都得啦"},{"pid":"7529ec40581b3c52353ada0d17ae7e17117b9922","tid":505251,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打嘅意見，如果以容易上手，部機好用、唔易壞為前提，應該點取捨？<br />\n<br />\n如果用MacBook或者MacBook pro，行Mac OS，係咪要下載好多Apps？有排搞？"},{"pid":"dd272a2e198ded461653549b941d2878695ee950","tid":505251,"uid":116563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝巴打嘅意見，如果以容易上手，部機好用、唔易壞為前提，應該點取捨？<br />\n<br />\n如果用MacBook或者MacBook pro，行Mac OS，係咪要下載好多Apps？有排搞？</blockquote><br />\n其實你要用d 咩apps<br />\nword 果d 肯google 下都有 <br />\n其實唔難 <br />\n<br />\nipad pro 始終行ios 同mac os 好唔同<br />\n你諗下邊個os岩你多d好過"},{"pid":"886ab148b006fc7d8aed51eaf5a909bd1556a3f2","tid":505251,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝巴打嘅意見，如果以容易上手，部機好用、唔易壞為前提，應該點取捨？<br />\n<br />\n如果用MacBook或者MacBook pro，行Mac OS，係咪要下載好多Apps？有排搞？</blockquote><br />\n其實你要用d 咩apps<br />\nword 果d 肯google 下都有 <br />\n其實唔難 <br />\n<br />\nipad pro 始終行ios 同mac os 好唔同<br />\n你諗下邊個os岩你多d好過</blockquote><br />\n早兩年屋企由PC轉用mac機，想保留舊PC啲資料，所以裝parallel，又再裝MS Office，其他例如Anti-virus，其他應用軟件，結果搞咗我幾日&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n印象中，iPad幾乎即買即用（itune back-up咗），而且我部iPad都好鬼舊，所以都想換，搞到心大心細&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n巴打對於兩套OS有乜意見？之前好似聽過話，唔知邊套OS唔會再發展，可能無乜前途&hellip;係咪堅料？"},{"pid":"f173286c8378207a4262452998f8228df35477af","tid":505251,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"做野咪用ipad"},{"pid":"6f9cefcc5f9fd5219a46238b84cdfcf7f1b7bac9","tid":505251,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d3fe47180c09aa62c8decf771518b38e90ad9eb","tid":505251,"uid":56204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:10:40.000Z","msg":"出trip重點梗係輕<br />\n更何況文書機使鬼咁勁spec<br />\nMacbook 12&rdquo;好好j"}]}